{"word":"Jeshua","slug":"jeshua","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jeshua</b> <a href=\"#/H3442\">H3442</a><br/><a href=\"#/H3443\">H3443</a> <br/> 1. Called Jeshuah<br/> - A priest, head of the ninth course<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=24&verse=11'>1Ch 24:11</a> <br/> - Nine hundred and seventy-three of his descendants returned from Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=36'>Ezr 2:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=39'>Neh 7:39</a> <br/> 2. A Levite<br/> - Had charge of the tithes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=15'>2Ch 31:15</a> <br/> - His descendants returned with Ezra from Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=40'>Ezr 2:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=43'>Neh 7:43</a> <br/> 3. Called Joshua<br/> - A priest who accompanied Zerubbabel from Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=2'>Ezr 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=7'>Neh 7:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=1'>Neh 12:1</a> <br/> - Descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=10'>Neh 12:10</a> <br/> - Rebuilt the altar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=2'>Ezr 3:2</a> <br/> - Rebuilt the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=13'>Ezr 3:13</a> <br/> - Contends with those who sought to defeat the rebuilding<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=4&verse=3'>Ezr 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=5&verse=2'>Ezr 5:2</a> <br/> 4. Father of Jozabad<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=33'>Ezr 8:33</a><br/> 5. Son of Pahath-Moab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=6'>Ezr 2:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=11'>Neh 7:11</a><br/> 6. Father of Ezer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=19'>Neh 3:19</a><br/> 7. A Levite who explained the law to the people when Ezra read it<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=7'>Neh 8:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=8'>Neh 12:8</a><br/> 8. A Levite who sealed Nehemiah's covenant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=9'>Neh 10:9</a><br/> 9. A city of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=26'>Neh 11:26</a><br/> 10. Joshua called<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=17'>Neh 8:17</a><br/> 11. Symbolic:<br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=3&verse=10'>Zec 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=6&verse=15'>Zec 6:15</a><br/><a href='S:Joshua'>Joshua</a> "}]}